<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Online Academy - Trang chủ</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff 0%, #00c6ff 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 80px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .course-card img {
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .badge-new {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }

        .badge-bestseller {
            background-color: #ffc107;
            color: #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-white shadow-sm fixed-top">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold text-primary" href="#">Online Academy</a>
            <form class="d-flex ms-auto" action="/search" method="GET">
                <input class="form-control me-2" type="search" placeholder="Tìm khóa học..." name="keyword">
                <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Tìm</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero mt-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Khám phá hàng trăm khóa học trực tuyến</h1>
            <p class="lead">Học bất cứ lúc nào, ở bất cứ đâu cùng giảng viên hàng đầu</p>
            <a href="#courses" class="btn btn-light mt-3 fw-semibold">Bắt đầu học ngay</a>
        </div>
    </section>



    {{{body}}}

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-4">
        <p class="mb-0">&copy; 2025 Online Academy. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
     
</body>

</html>